	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64566697">This story is only part of bigger chain of events. Canadian government sent all federal employees to work from home due to COVID. They are still mostly working from home in 2024. As the result, public transit, downtown businesses, and office real estate in Ottawa crashed and burned. They are now trying to force public servants back into the office, but compliance is low. Not in small part because due to office space downsides and moves there often not enough desks available for everyone. So people resorted to coffee-badging, This robot is part of enforcing office attendance.</div>
	</div>

